Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.29,0:00:05.81,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}メルエムに対し
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.29,0:00:05.81,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Alone? I'm impressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.81,0:00:09.30,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}時間稼ぎのために 勝負を挑んだプフは
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.81,0:00:09.30,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Where do you want to die?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.30,0:00:12.30,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}まだ　催眠状態にない人民達に
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.30,0:00:12.30,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I'll humor any requests.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.30,0:00:20.30,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}鱗粉を散布していた 急がねば　メルエム様が あれのことを思い出す前に…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.30,0:00:20.30,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I'd prefer a deserted wasteland, \Nwith no one nearby. Since I'll have you screaming \Nat the top of your lungs.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.82,0:01:50.30,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}一刻も早く 娘を抹殺しに向かいたいのに 何としても！ 今回が正真正銘　最後の機会！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.82,0:01:50.30,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Condition x And x Condition
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.27,0:03:28.32,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}パームは　ここに残ってる 女性４人を連れて来てくれ。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.27,0:03:28.32,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}A small clan, with Scarlet Eyes, \Nthat lived in the Lukso Province.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.32,0:03:30.88,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}あの４人　逃げてないの？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.32,0:03:30.88,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Five years ago, you attacked us.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.88,0:03:35.28,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ああ　ガムテープで 目と手を縛ったほうがいい。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.88,0:03:35.28,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Scarlet Eyes? What's that? The name of a treasure?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.28,0:03:38.78,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}俺を見られたら説明とか長くなる。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.28,0:03:38.78,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Sorry, doesn't ring a bell...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.78,0:03:45.77,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}そうね　分かったわ。 ところで　何で あいつら乗せて来たの？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.78,0:03:45.77,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}But five years ago, \NI was definitely a member. When you kill a completely \Ninnocent bystander, what are you people thinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.28,0:04:00.27,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}地下倉庫の奥に　娘が 捕らわれているってことだけ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.28,0:04:00.27,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Nothing at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.27,0:04:03.78,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}王か護衛軍に伝えてくれればいい。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.27,0:04:03.78,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Scum!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.78,0:04:10.32,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}俺達が交渉したいって 言ってるってな。 その後は自由だ。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.78,0:04:10.32,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}You will atone through death!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.32,0:04:18.27,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}どうせ罠があんだろ？ それは王に言うぜ。 言わなきゃ不自然だし 俺が疑われる。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.32,0:04:18.27,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Fools like you are the reason \NI never get sick of killing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.27,0:04:23.28,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ああ。 いや それ以前　敵のパシリ自体
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.27,0:04:23.28,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Wanna know what I enjoy most?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.28,0:04:29.28,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}王の逆鱗に触れかねねえ！ 誰がやるかよ　そんなこと
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.28,0:04:29.28,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Denying those who come \Nin search of revenge!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.29,0:04:52.86,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}プフを抹消してでも 見ておいたほうが…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.29,0:04:52.86,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Those chains are dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.86,0:04:59.78,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}パーム。 大丈夫
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.86,0:04:59.78,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I don't know what kind \Nof trick he used on them, but they hold an abnormal amount of Nen.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.79,0:05:07.29,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ウェルフィン これが終わったら自由なんだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.79,0:05:07.29,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Strike first to win!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.27,0:05:12.27,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ジャイロに会いに行けよ。 えっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.27,0:05:12.27,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Got him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.27,0:05:23.79,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}気安く　あいつの名前 呼ぶんじゃ　ねえ！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.27,0:05:23.79,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}That's a surprise...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.79,0:05:27.28,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}てめぇに何が分かる　あぁ!?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.79,0:05:27.28,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}After taking that punch, \Nhe still has the strength to attack?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.28,0:05:31.79,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}分かるよ　ザイカハル。 あっ。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.28,0:05:31.79,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}But his left arm is useless now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.80,0:05:48.28,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}何で…。 何で　俺の…。 前の…。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.80,0:05:48.28,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Unscathed? Impossible... Considering the amount \Nof Nen in those chains, he must be a Manipulator or a Conjurer...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.28,0:05:51.78,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}誰にも言ってないはず
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.28,0:05:51.78,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I would guess the former.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.78,0:05:56.89,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}俺は多分　もう 昔の名前　思い出せないけど
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.78,0:05:56.89,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}But only an Enhancer should be \Nable to block my attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.89,0:05:59.29,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}仲間さ。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.89,0:05:59.29,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}What is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.29,0:06:02.79,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}仲間？ 前のな。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.29,0:06:02.79,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Was that punch
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.27,0:06:15.77,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}俺達　ＮＧＬの。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.27,0:06:15.77,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}That wasn't even funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.89,0:06:20.30,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}違うか？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.89,0:06:20.30,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Don't worry. That was twenty percent of my strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.30,0:06:23.80,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}うっ　うぅ…。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.30,0:06:23.80,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}This time, I'll use half!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.78,0:06:29.29,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ブロヴーダも　前世を 忘れているだけで　仲間のはず。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.78,0:06:29.29,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.77,0:06:46.77,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}イカルゴ　何で てめぇは知ってんだよ？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.77,0:06:46.77,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.30,0:06:55.78,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ジャイロが 生きてんのを知らなきゃ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.30,0:06:55.78,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.78,0:07:00.89,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}そんな言い方しねえだろ！ ああ　確かに。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.78,0:07:00.89,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Damn, he keeps darting around. But...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.89,0:07:07.78,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}でも　知ってるんじゃなくて そうとしか思えないからだよ。 ん？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.89,0:07:07.78,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I'll regret not using that \Nchance to chain you up?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.30,0:07:15.80,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}あいつが ただ　消化されるわけないだろ。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.30,0:07:15.80,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Stop making excuses, \Nand give me your best shot. You're wasting my time.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.28,0:07:36.29,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}チクショウ　チクショウ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.28,0:07:36.29,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}A smoke screen? His presence has disappeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.29,0:07:39.79,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}チクショウ！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.29,0:07:39.79,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}He's using In!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.79,0:08:00.80,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}１０分過ぎても　ピトーが 戻る気配なんて　全くねえぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.79,0:08:00.80,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}No one can withstand a full-strength Big Bang Impact.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.28,0:08:18.28,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}降りろ。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.28,0:08:18.28,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I didn't think you knew how to use In.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.77,0:08:31.36,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}外に出れば 状況は　ひと目で分かるはずだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.77,0:08:31.36,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}was intended to conceal both your \Nphysical body and your presence. However... I, too, can use In.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.88,0:08:56.77,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}むかつくが イカルゴの言う通りだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.88,0:08:56.77,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}These chains were fortified \Nwith a Conjurer's Nen. Meaning I can use In to \Nrender them invisible.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.77,0:09:00.27,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ジャイロが殺されて 終わるわけがねえ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.77,0:09:00.27,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}So you kept the chains out to trick us into thinking they were real?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.29,0:09:05.29,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}なら　奴らは敵
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.29,0:09:05.29,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Precisely.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.29,0:09:10.80,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}目を覚まさせてくれた礼だ メッセンジャーくらい やってやるよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.29,0:09:10.80,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I pretended to be a Manipulator \Nusing Nen-controlled chains, so my enemies would only be \Nalert to the visible chains.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.29,0:09:18.79,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ん？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.29,0:09:18.79,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}While you were making empty threats, my chains were already \Nwrapped around your body.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.80,0:09:32.80,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}止まれ！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.80,0:09:32.80,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}You've been captured.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.79,0:09:39.29,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ユピー殿？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.79,0:09:39.29,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Damn... But how? He has an Enhancer's defensive power...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.78,0:09:44.30,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}早速　護衛軍のお出ましか
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.78,0:09:44.30,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}And the Nen in his conjured \Nchains is incredibly strong...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.34,0:09:55.28,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ユピー殿　至急
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.34,0:09:55.28,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}That's impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.28,0:09:58.78,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}王に　お伝えせねば ならないことがございます。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.28,0:09:58.78,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}A Nen user can only fully master \Ntheir innate category.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.29,0:10:10.80,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}地下倉庫に？ はっ。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.29,0:10:10.80,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Let me illuminate you, before \Nsending you to the other side.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.32,0:10:21.79,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}はい　一刻も早く 王様へお伝えください。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.32,0:10:21.79,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Those eyes...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.30,0:10:28.30,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}なるほど　勝負なんだから
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.30,0:10:28.30,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}There were a bunch of them, \Nin the middle of nowhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.30,0:10:31.80,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}王に伝えなくとも問題なしだ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.30,0:10:31.80,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}The boss really liked those eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.80,0:10:33.79,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}プフの奴
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.80,0:10:33.79,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}They were pretty strong!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.79,0:10:37.32,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ここまで考えての提案だとしたら 大したもんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.79,0:10:37.32,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Then, you're a survivor?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.28,0:10:46.78,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}はっ。 取りあえず プフが戻ったら知らせねえと
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.28,0:10:46.78,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Let's see which is stronger, your grudge or my power!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.79,0:10:56.29,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}それにしても　ピトーは 一体　何してやがるんだ？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.79,0:10:56.29,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Is that all you can think about? You'll never be able to break these chains!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.81,0:11:19.30,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ユピー殿！ あ？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.81,0:11:19.30,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}When my eyes turn scarlet, \NI become a Specialist. What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.30,0:11:26.29,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}お聞きしたいことが。 何だ？ 前世の記憶はありますか？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.30,0:11:26.29,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}When I am a Specialist, I wield full control over \Nevery category of Nen.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.29,0:11:29.29,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}キメラに　なる前の。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.29,0:11:29.29,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}And this is my power...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.29,0:11:32.80,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}あ？　ねえよ　そんなもん。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.29,0:11:32.80,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Absolute Mastery\NEmperor Time Emperor Time!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.39,0:11:48.80,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ユピー殿。 おい！　いいかげんに…。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.39,0:11:48.80,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Yes, when I heard about conjuring, that was the first thing that came to mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.80,0:11:50.30,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}うわっ。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.80,0:11:50.30,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Chains, huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.30,0:11:55.80,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ん？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.30,0:11:55.80,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Because there's evil running \Nloose that needs to be
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.80,0:11:59.29,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}俺を攻撃すれば　反撃する。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.80,0:11:59.29,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}chained down to hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.29,0:12:01.81,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}いくつか質問する。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.29,0:12:01.81,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Really, now?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.81,0:12:08.86,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}５秒以内に答えろ。 グゥ…。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.81,0:12:08.86,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I get the feeling that you're \Nactually just chaining yourself. What would you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.80,0:12:15.30,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}調子　乗ってんじゃねえぞ！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.80,0:12:15.30,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Hey! Wait up! I'm your teacher!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.30,0:12:17.30,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}クソが！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.30,0:12:17.30,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I'm not finished talking! Hold it right there...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.81,0:12:34.81,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}勝負…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.81,0:12:34.81,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Man, you're so stubborn.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.32,0:12:45.79,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}足りぬ　何かが…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.32,0:12:45.79,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Really?! Yeah, you only hear what you want to hear.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.29,0:13:22.79,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}そうだ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.29,0:13:22.79,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Come up with a rule for your chains. One that you are prepared to follow.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.31,0:13:39.79,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}余は　誰かと戦っていた そして余は
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.31,0:13:39.79,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}It's a double-edged sword. If you break the rule you set, \Nyou could lose your Nen.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.79,0:13:43.78,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}まだ　勝っていない
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.79,0:13:43.78,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}My objective is to find my brethren's Scarlet Eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.78,0:13:47.78,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}その者に　一度も
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.78,0:13:47.78,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}and to capture the spiders. I want chains that are
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.30,0:13:53.80,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}うっ。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.30,0:13:53.80,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}unbreakable by the spiders, \Nthe Phantom Troupe. The spiders will be my only targets.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.81,0:14:18.28,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}クッ 予想以上に時間がかかった
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.81,0:14:18.28,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I'll stake my life on it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.28,0:14:22.37,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}もう　とっくに ピトーは戻っているはず
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.28,0:14:22.37,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Hey, Kurapika...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.37,0:14:24.87,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}王が　焦れてなければいいが
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.37,0:14:24.87,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}When your eyes are scarlet, \Nyour aura spikes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.30,0:14:30.79,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ユピーは？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.30,0:14:30.79,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Let's try water divination again!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.79,0:14:35.29,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ユピーは　どこです？ ん？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.79,0:14:35.29,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}A Specialist?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.29,0:14:39.31,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}あれは…。 あっ。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.29,0:14:39.31,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}You have full control over \Nevery other category?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.79,0:14:50.79,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ユピー？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.79,0:14:50.79,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Holy Chain: Healing Thumb
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.28,0:15:00.78,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}そ…　そんな…。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.28,0:15:00.78,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I can use enhanced self-healing to completely recover a broken arm.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.30,0:15:20.80,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}もう　大丈夫。 どういう意味だ？　パーム。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.30,0:15:20.80,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}While you fought the Mafia \Nand the Shadow Beasts, the other spiders stayed out of it altogether.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.81,0:15:30.38,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}王！　メルエム様！ ユピーが殺されました。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.81,0:15:30.38,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}That told me you preferred to fight alone, and that they trusted that \Nyour strength would prevail.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.38,0:15:33.80,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}敵にも　かなりの手だれが まだ　います！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.38,0:15:33.80,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I prefer to fight one-on-one.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.80,0:15:38.29,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ピトーは？ はっ…。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.80,0:15:38.29,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}That made you a perfect target.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.29,0:15:46.32,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}いえ　まだ。 ならば　ようやく 余も始動できるわけだな。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.29,0:15:46.32,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}An Enhancer who was confident \Nin his offense and defense.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.32,0:15:49.34,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}い…　いえ　メルエム様！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.32,0:15:49.34,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}You met every condition I \Nrequired for my first target.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.34,0:15:55.31,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}状況が変わりました！ やめると申すか？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.34,0:15:55.31,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Because then I could test if my Chain Jail
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.31,0:15:56.81,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}うっ。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.31,0:15:56.81,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}would be effective on the rest of the Troupe.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.79,0:16:04.78,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ならば余の勝利。 洗いざらい話してもらうぞ。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.79,0:16:04.78,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Chain Jail forcefully activates Zetsu \Nupon any Troupe member it ensnares.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.78,0:16:09.30,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}うっ！ それでいいのか？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.78,0:16:09.30,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}It also paralyzes them.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.39,0:16:16.80,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}「もう　大丈夫」って どういう意味だ？　パーム。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.39,0:16:16.80,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}So that's why I can't muster any aura...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.80,0:16:21.80,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}キルアの結論は 王にとって彼女は特別。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.80,0:16:21.80,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Zetsu nullifies aura.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.80,0:16:26.31,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}でも　護衛軍では 意見が分かれている。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.80,0:16:26.31,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Meaning you'd need to use
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.31,0:16:29.33,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}なぜなら
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.31,0:16:29.33,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}physical strength alone to break these chains. Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.33,0:16:37.31,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ピトーは　そのコを救い　守り プフは殺そうとした。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.33,0:16:37.31,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}If the Troupe member with the most \Nphysical strength cannot break the chains, the others will certainly be \Nunable to escape Chain Jail.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.29,0:16:41.80,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}つまり　彼女は
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.29,0:16:41.80,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}His forced activation of Zetsu here is bad...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.80,0:16:45.29,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}王にとって　もろ刃の剣。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.80,0:16:45.29,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Aura is the basis of all Nen.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.29,0:16:53.30,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}いやいや… 俺には信じられねえ。 王の意思に逆らって 護衛軍の統率が乱れるなんて
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.29,0:16:53.30,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}If it's sealed off, you can't use your power.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.30,0:16:55.32,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}あり得ねえよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.30,0:16:55.32,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}A technique for sealing Nen...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.32,0:17:01.31,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}そう？ でも　なら　何で 私や　あなたは　ここにいるの？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.32,0:17:01.31,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}This guy thought everything through.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.87,0:17:14.30,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}普通のキメラなら「あり得ない」が いろいろ起こっている。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.87,0:17:14.30,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}It looks as though my enhanced fist
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.30,0:17:17.31,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}絶対と言い切れる根拠はある？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.30,0:17:17.31,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}is slightly stronger than your physical brawn.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.31,0:17:19.79,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}うん。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.31,0:17:19.79,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}That's valuable information.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.79,0:17:28.32,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ごめんね でも　私が言いたいのは 王への忠誠と　護衛軍の分裂は
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.79,0:17:28.32,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Then I can beat every Troupe member \Nbarehanded, provided I've chained them.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.32,0:17:34.79,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}必ずしも矛盾しないってこと。 王が大事にしている人間がいる。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.32,0:17:34.79,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Tell me everything you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.79,0:17:39.30,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}「だから　その人を守る」と 「だから　その人を殺す」は
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.79,0:17:39.30,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Where are the other spiders?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.30,0:17:42.30,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}どちらも成り立つのよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.30,0:17:42.30,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Kill me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.80,0:17:50.30,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}それと　「もう　大丈夫」は どう　つながるんだよ？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.80,0:17:50.30,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}What abilities do they have?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.36,0:17:55.80,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}王の最初の「円」から およそ２０分経過。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.36,0:17:55.80,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Kill me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.31,0:18:13.88,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}最初の「円」の時 私は　このコを背負ってた。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.31,0:18:13.88,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}It makes me sick...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.88,0:18:17.30,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}王が そのことに気付いていたなら
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.88,0:18:17.30,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}The sensation left on my hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.30,0:18:20.30,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}まず　私の元に来たはず。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.30,0:18:20.30,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}The grating sound of each strike.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.30,0:18:24.81,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}そうしなかったのは 髪の毛で覆っていたから。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.30,0:18:24.81,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}The smell of blood! It all throws my senses into disarray...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.81,0:18:33.35,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}背負っていたものを　人と 認識できなかったと考えられる。 そこまではいい？ うん。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.81,0:18:33.35,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}How can you do these things, \Nyet feel and think nothing at all?! Answer me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.35,0:18:38.30,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}論理的だし異論ねえよ 話は全く見えないけどな。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.35,0:18:38.30,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Kill me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.81,0:18:49.28,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}それって　ナックルとメレオロン 見殺しにして
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.81,0:18:49.28,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}This is your last chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.28,0:18:51.80,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}交渉しねえってことかよ？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.28,0:18:51.80,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I just placed a conditional \Nbond on your heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.80,0:19:01.79,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}まさか… 交渉は　もちろんするわよ。 ただし　できる限りの時間を稼ぐの そのためにも
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.80,0:19:01.79,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}If you break the rule I set, the bond will activate, crushing your heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.79,0:19:06.30,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}このコは　王に見つからない場所に かくまう必要があるわ。
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.79,0:19:06.30,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}The rule is that you must answer my question honestly.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.30,0:19:14.79,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}王が　死ぬまで。
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.30,0:19:14.79,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Abide by that rule, and I shall \Nallow you to live a bit longer. Where are the other spiders?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.90,0:19:47.80,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}何で 「もう　大丈夫」になるんだよ？ もっと　はっきり教えてくれ！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.90,0:19:47.80,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I spent too much time in that state...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.85,0:20:04.81,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}数時間のうちに
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.85,0:20:04.81,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Why didn't you call? Are you okay? Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.81,0:20:07.29,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}王は死ぬ。
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.81,0:20:07.29,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I'm glad to hear that... What about on your side?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.80,0:20:19.32,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}もっと奥がいいわ。
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.80,0:20:19.32,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I see. I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.29,0:20:56.29,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}私達は残酷よ。
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.29,0:20:56.29,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}A chain user...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.87,0:21:11.29,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}いえ　それ以上に…。
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.87,0:21:11.29,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}But in a one-on-one fight, he is most \Nvulnerable to those two categories. Many Conjurers give special powers
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.78,0:21:36.30,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ピトー　ピトー！ 一体どこです？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.78,0:21:36.30,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}If he fails to return by dawn, there will be a change in plans.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.30,0:21:40.28,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ピトー!! うっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.30,0:21:40.28,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Shalnark senses the danger, \Nas Uvogin fails to return.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.33,0:21:48.88,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}あっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.33,0:21:48.88,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Their leader, Chrollo, prepares to terminate the chain user.
